Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.05,0:02:01.81,"Sign",,0,0,0,,"Golden Pavilion"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.35,0:02:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no mistaking that this is my handwriting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.31,0:02:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Sky islands... Naval base G-8...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.26,0:02:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And this gold...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.22,0:02:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If this is all true, everything makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.43,0:02:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If I could go back to Cocoyashi Village,\NI should be able to figure everything out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.80,0:02:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But there aren't any decent ships.\NHow can I go back...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.60,0:02:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And, of all the places, I'm in the Grand Line?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.35,0:02:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,According to this sea chart,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.63,0:02:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,you can't exit the Grand Line midway\Nthrough to get to the East Blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.42,0:02:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What'd you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.72,0:02:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the captain, you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.01,0:02:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,At any rate, that was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.93,0:02:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If I hadn't remembered things, I would've\Nremained Usopp's underling forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.85,0:02:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! I'm never gonna believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.73,0:02:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what anyone says,\NI am the great pirate, Captain Usopp,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.82,0:02:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,who leads 8,000 underlings\Nin the Usopp Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.11,0:03:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the spirit! That's our Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.45,0:03:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're the sniper of\Nthe Straw Hat Pirates, Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.45,0:03:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot... Now he's above me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.83,0:03:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy is a monster just like me,\Nand yet he's a captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.71,0:03:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.50,0:03:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh! Don't come this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.38,0:03:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you still acting like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.89,0:03:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's play like we always do!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.05,0:03:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the ship's doctor, and yet I was\Nreally doing something like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.73,0:03:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, this is your signature party piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.14,0:03:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You did it whenever we had a party.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.48,0:03:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,A one! A two!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.65,0:03:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,--A one, two, three!\N--That rubber monkey said\Nthat he regained his memories,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.82,0:03:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,but he acts just like he did before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.44,0:03:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It means that our captain doesn't change,\Nno matter what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.82,0:03:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, let's sing the usual song!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.07,0:03:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I'm part of a pirate crew, if I'm\Nnobody, they might just slave drive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.87,0:03:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,On top of that, being around monsters like them,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.87,0:03:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,no matter how many lives\Nyou have, it won't be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.79,0:03:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.58,0:03:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that everyone lost their memories.\NTheir memories were taken away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.92,0:03:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And the culprit, after all, is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.47,0:04:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's that damn brat?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.80,0:04:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, what does he want with our memories?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.97,0:04:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Good question.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.76,0:04:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.85,0:04:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.94,0:04:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to bring back Nami\Nand Zoro. Let's go, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.35,0:04:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.15,0:04:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's wait until morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.94,0:04:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Why, Robin?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.86,0:04:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We've never been to this place.\NOn top of that, it's the dead of night.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.11,0:04:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't be that easy to find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.53,0:04:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.16,0:04:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't it be better to\Nsleep a little until dawn?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.62,0:04:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That boy seems to have learned a lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.96,0:04:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think we have to worry\Nabout him showing up again tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.38,0:04:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! We'll leave tomorrow morning then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.30,0:04:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,--Hold on.\N--Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.05,0:04:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm all for bringing back that lady, Nami-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.89,0:04:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,but I don't see why we're\Ngoing after that Zoro guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.72,0:04:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Me neither! If you wanna go,\Nyou two can go by yourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.56,0:04:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.56,0:04:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you guys saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.98,0:04:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We're saying, why do we have to include Zoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.40,0:05:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a pirate hunter, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.90,0:05:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do we have to go to the\Ntrouble of chasing after him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.12,0:05:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why else? It's because he's one of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.99,0:05:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you say he's one of us... Right...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.29,0:05:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't feel that way even a bit.\NYou know that, too, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.92,0:05:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that he left in a hurry is proof of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.30,0:05:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Usopp is the sniper. Sanji is the cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.01,0:05:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Chopper is the ship doctor.\NRobin is the archaeologist.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.76,0:05:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami is the navigator.\NAnd Zoro is the swordsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.89,0:05:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We, the Straw Hat Pirates, can't leave\Nanyone out, not even one person!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.27,0:05:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We just have to get the\Nswordsman's memories back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.32,0:05:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If so, then I just have to beat up that brat,\Njust like I did earlier, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.99,0:05:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Chopper?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.03,0:05:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, looks like we'll have a busy day tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.74,0:05:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get some sleep while we can!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.79,0:05:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The key to solving all the\Nmysteries is on that island...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.80,0:06:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I underestimated Monkey D. Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.76,0:06:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If I make an enemy out of him,\NI could be in big trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.27,0:06:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'll definitely make my wish come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.23,0:06:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to do so, I have to make friends, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.94,0:06:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can't go wrong\Nwith a skilled swordsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.84,0:06:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. It's different from yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.88,0:06:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Zoro, a pirate hunter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.97,0:06:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If I carelessly get closer,\NI may make another blunder.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.18,0:06:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. I won't do it now.\NThere'll be another chance, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.06,0:06:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, when that time comes,\NI'll have you do your job but good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.07,0:07:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's said that the All Blue has\Nfoodstuffs from around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.37,0:07:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to dream of going to that legendary sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.21,0:07:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't ask for your help!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.54,0:07:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't think of any reason\Nfor you to be kind to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.96,0:07:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...? Why did you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.96,0:07:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you had the same dream as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.13,0:07:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Restaurant?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.34,0:07:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I was thinking that I'd build a\Nrestaurant as my final purpose in life...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.39,0:07:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, then, I'll help\Nyou do that. So don't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.60,0:07:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha! It's impossible for a\Nweak little brat like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.28,0:07:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll become strong, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.90,0:07:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way that I'd leave that\Ndamn annoying geezer, my benefactor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.74,0:07:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...? What happened to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.92,0:08:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Pepper, Carrot, Onion... I wonder what\Nthe Usopp Pirates are doing now...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.30,0:08:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! Let's go, Usopp Pirates!\NTo protect this village's peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.68,0:08:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So what adventure are\Nyou going to tell me today?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.06,0:08:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.40,0:08:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The story of when I fought the giant\Ngoldfish at the South Pole when I was five!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.77,0:08:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Goldfish?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.23,0:08:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! What first shocked me\Nwas the immense size of its poop!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.49,0:08:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It was so big that I landed on it,\Nthinking it was solid ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.16,0:08:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a dream that I wanted to\Nbecome a pirate like my old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.42,0:08:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But to think that I became a pirate\Nwhen I had to leave them to do so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.46,0:08:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Why am I with humans?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.68,0:08:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The only ones I trusted were\NDr. Hiriluk and Doctorine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.18,0:09:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Even among the reindeers, I had\Nno friends. I was always alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.60,0:09:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I will never shoot you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.19,0:09:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Dr. Hiriluk!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.40,0:09:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.20,0:09:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, there's no disease\Nin this world that can't be cured.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.82,0:09:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what anyone says about me,\NI'll save this country as a doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.00,0:09:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I raised this skull\Ntowards all the diseases!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.00,0:09:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Skull...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.13,0:09:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! This is a symbol of\Nthe belief that nothing is impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.67,0:09:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,By raising this, I'll fight just like pirates do!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.89,0:09:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,My friends? On top of that, six of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.35,0:09:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe that I'm the\Nship's doctor for a pirate ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.27,0:09:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But what if it's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.53,0:09:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,They won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.70,0:09:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,My dream won't be lost. It must\Nbe the same for you guys, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.23,0:10:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami, Zoro, just wait. I'm coming for you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.15,0:10:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone! Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.28,0:10:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been up for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.07,0:10:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The cook and the ship's doctor\Nsaid that they're coming along.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.49,0:10:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.04,0:10:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't just abandon that lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.83,0:10:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, Robin-san needs a bodyguard, too, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.46,0:10:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If someone gets injured, you'll be in\Ntrouble without me, a doctor, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.84,0:10:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm taking on the job of guarding the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.01,0:10:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,--Come along with us too, Usopp!\N--Like I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.14,0:11:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, actually, I've got "My Heart Will\NStop Once on the Island" disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.85,0:11:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,--Ow, ow, ow...\N--Just come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.77,0:11:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that Usopp, a brave warrior\Nof the sea, has his moments.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.27,0:11:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.52,0:11:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! We'll all go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.07,0:11:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot! I just got too elated...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.05,0:11:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So, how are we gonna get to the island?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.41,0:11:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,How about using a raft?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.40,0:11:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's a good idea.\NWe're counting on you, Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.94,0:11:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Why me?! I'm Captain Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.46,0:11:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.54,0:11:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,At the very least, I'm a sniper!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.99,0:11:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Either way, there's no way I could\Ndo stuff like a shipwright would do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.47,0:11:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,To make a raft, all you have to do\Nis to put logs together, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.50,0:11:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.03,0:11:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Are those knots done right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.44,0:11:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's pretty much it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.64,0:11:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey... Knots like that will untie\Nright away and the logs will drift apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.35,0:11:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If we're gonna make one,\NI want a cool-looking one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.07,0:11:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,How about this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.65,0:11:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No! This one is cooler!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.91,0:12:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,According to my tastes, it should be this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.28,0:12:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.33,0:12:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys call yourselves pirates when\Nyou can't even make a decent raft?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.16,0:12:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.62,0:12:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What amazing workmanship!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.42,0:12:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Usopp has his moments!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.63,0:12:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I admit, I have no idea myself why I built it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.05,0:12:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! We're off!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.56,0:12:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for letting me stay.\NHow much do I owe you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.23,0:12:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.02,0:12:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What? I'm your inn guest\Nwho stayed here last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.61,0:12:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.19,0:12:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't know her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.86,0:12:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it possible that she's a thief?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.87,0:12:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.53,0:12:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on a sec! I'm your guest!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.20,0:12:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I met all three of you yesterday, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.25,0:12:57.64,"Sign",,0,0,0,,"Inn" "Inn"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.16,0:12:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys really don't remember me? Manager?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.38,0:12:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Manager? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.05,0:13:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the manager, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.72,0:13:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.64,0:13:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm lucky that I got a free stay out of it,\Nbut what on earth is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.39,0:13:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Could this be...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.48,0:13:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.57,0:13:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys lost your memories, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.44,0:13:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I was like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.82,0:13:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,...yesterday...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.95,0:13:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,About yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.03,0:13:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I think they came to this village.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.71,0:13:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,A moss-headed swordsman and a woman\Non a strange vehicle. Did you see them?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.54,0:13:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday... what did I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.88,0:13:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You too?! Seriously, what the heck\Nis with the people on this island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.67,0:13:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,To think no one even\Nremembers about yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.51,0:13:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What carefree people!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.22,0:13:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it an issue of being carefree?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.18,0:13:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't complain about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.18,0:13:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,--What?\N--We, too, can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.56,0:13:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The cause might be the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.27,0:14:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What're we gonna do? It'll be kinda\Ntough finding them in this situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.94,0:14:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, then. Let's go back to the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.15,0:14:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Staying on this creepy island won't\Ndo us any good. Right? Let's go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.08,0:14:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.21,0:14:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.62,0:14:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.55,0:14:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,This is terrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.93,0:14:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you run away, Nami?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.43,0:14:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never give this to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.85,0:14:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you kill me, I won't give this to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.73,0:14:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say that! There's no way\Nwe'd hurt a pretty lady like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.48,0:14:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't even lay a finger on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.11,0:14:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Though I want to, to be honest...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.94,0:14:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of disease does he have?\NDo something about it, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.49,0:14:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's definitely a serious condition,\Nbut I'm also sure that there's no cure for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.74,0:14:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, let's make a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.95,0:14:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,A deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.87,0:14:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you 10% of this treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.33,0:14:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So take me to Cocoyashi Village using that ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.83,0:15:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,--No.\N--Then, how about 20%?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.21,0:15:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,--No.\N--Then, 30%!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.51,0:15:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,--No.\N--Pretending that there's no tomorrow, 50%!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.30,0:15:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.76,0:15:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Just how much do you want to rip me off for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.64,0:15:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You love treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.31,0:15:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way you're thinking\Nof sharing any of it with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.44,0:15:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you tell what I'm thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.69,0:15:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Because we're friends, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.57,0:15:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, friends with you guys?! Give me a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.57,0:15:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way we're friends!\NThe negotiations broke down. See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.91,0:15:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Please move.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.71,0:15:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't. Nami, you come along with us, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.04,0:15:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! Why would I go with you guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.97,0:15:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Please move!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.01,0:15:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.30,0:15:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Navigator.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.05,0:15:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been feeling something's odd too,\Nsince you came to this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.60,0:15:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.98,0:16:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.82,0:16:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,A child with a strange horn...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.61,0:16:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I kicked his ass. And then,\Nsmoke came out from the horn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.41,0:16:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,When I thought it went into my body...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.04,0:16:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The captain's memories came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.58,0:16:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No way. Wasn't it a dream or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.09,0:16:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true. I saw it clearly with my own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.09,0:16:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That damn brat... I feel like I saw\Nhim the night before last, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.30,0:16:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did he come twice?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.39,0:16:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe because he couldn't steal\Nall your memories in one shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.68,0:16:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Even with just what I know,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.27,0:16:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,you guys have experienced an\Nincredible number of adventures.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.27,0:16:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,He couldn't eat them all in one shot, so he\Nreturned yesterday on an empty stomach?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.57,0:16:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that's what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.65,0:16:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? I wonder if memories taste good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.95,0:16:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Then that kid is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.95,0:16:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.33,0:17:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, then! Let's kick that kid's ass again
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.50,0:17:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and get everyone's memories back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.83,0:17:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If we do that, Zoro will\Nprobably come back, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.72,0:17:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm doubtful whether it'd go that smoothly,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.67,0:17:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,but we have to get even with that damn brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.51,0:17:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we forget about Zoro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.01,0:17:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we regain our\Nmemories by some chance,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.51,0:17:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,it's kinda unsettling to be on\Nthe same ship as a pirate hunter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.02,0:17:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Zoro is the swordsman. Nami is the navigator.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.31,0:17:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of them are our friends that we need.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.02,0:17:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you say so, I'm in a bind!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.03,0:17:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,To think that I'm one of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.53,0:17:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who'll be in\Na bigger bind without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.49,0:17:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Without a navigator,\Nthe ship can't go anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.41,0:17:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Robin, can you tell where that kid is?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.16,0:17:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... there's a place that I want to check out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.67,0:17:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay then! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.09,0:17:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey! My gold is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.80,0:17:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let a lady carry stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.09,0:17:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can be with you, Nami-san,\Nthis is no trouble at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.51,0:17:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh... I have a bad feeling about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.81,0:18:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what they say, they all follow Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.27,0:18:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if it's true that I now have friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.81,0:18:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you doing?! Hurry up, Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.36,0:18:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.64,0:18:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wanna eat, help yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.23,0:18:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true that I am hungry,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.15,0:18:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,but I don't eat this kind of stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.11,0:18:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.23,0:18:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Why aren't you asking who I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.49,0:18:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah... People on this island\Ndon't even remember their own names.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.57,0:19:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You thought it was no use asking, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.33,0:19:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You set out on a journey to become\Nthe world's strongest, right, mister?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.08,0:19:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, to you, Monkey D. Luffy is\Nthe perfect opponent, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.92,0:19:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Luffy! Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.38,0:19:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That straw hat guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.93,0:19:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised that Roronoa Zoro\Ncouldn't perceive his strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.89,0:19:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't perceive it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.73,0:19:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. In the East Blue,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.19,0:19:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,he destroyed the vicious Fishman pirate group, the Arlong Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.65,0:19:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Here in the Grand Line,\Nhe brought down Crocodile,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.32,0:19:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,one of the Seven Great Pirates, all by himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.86,0:19:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Seven Great Pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.28,0:19:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.03,0:19:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,On the sky islands, he even\Nbeat up the god named Eneru.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.29,0:19:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah... He went on a\Nrampage in a Navy base, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.37,0:19:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Against Luffy, even the\NNavy throws up its hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.96,0:19:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen a pirate like that before!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.13,0:19:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't talk nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.88,0:20:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have time to listen to lies like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.26,0:20:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, now you want to fight Luffy, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.52,0:20:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You jerk! What on earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.12,0:20:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? What's this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.80,0:20:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that weird brat here? This is kinda creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.34,0:20:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I wonder if I caught a cold or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.60,0:20:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been feeling a chill for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.10,0:20:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish we had a doctor at a time like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.52,0:20:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.23,0:21:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet these people are trying to take me\Nto a deserted place and steal the gold!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.53,0:21:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let that happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.74,0:21:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami-san has been giving me\Npassionate eyes all this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.66,0:21:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt! She fell in love with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.00,0:21:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,--Wink!\N--Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.00,0:21:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a sign that he's gonna steal\Nthe gold?! What a creepy guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.05,0:21:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.55,0:21:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, a butterfly!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.05,0:21:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you find something out, Robin?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.93,0:21:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured out the culprit who\Ntook your memories away...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.85,0:21:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No... I mean, the real culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.10,0:21:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That damn brat isn't the culprit?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.11,0:21:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let's head to the Sea God's Palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.03,0:21:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sea God's Palace?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.74,0:21:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.99,0:21:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm calling it that for now...
